PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of the following persons as directors of Marine Atlantic Inc. to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years. (SHARON GELDART of Moncton, New Brunswick, in the place of Lucille Riedle, who has resigned; HARRY E. WOODMAN of Glace Bay, Nova Scotia, in the place of John R. Coady, who has resigned; ARTHUR ROBERT SAMPSON of Sydney, Nova Scotia, in the place of Elsbeth L. Cassidy, who has resigned; and MARG FRISON of Marion Bridge, Nova Scotia, in the place of Philip R. Murray, whose term has expired)
